## MD5  
Return MD5 Hash for input String  

# C  
`void md5 (const char* str, char* digest);`  

# ASM  
`>PUSHW digest`  
`>PUSHW str`  

## RETURN VALUE  
CC  

## MD5Init  
Initialize a MD5 computation  

# C  
`hMD5 md5init ();`  

# ASM  
`>LIBCALL hLIBCRYPT,LIBCRYPT.MD5Init`  

## RETURN VALUE  
A = hMem To S.MD5
